ReusableEmailStatement.Title: We have received your Deposit!
ReusableEmailStatement.StatementText: I want to let you know that we have received your deposit and wanted to congratulate you on becoming an official part of the Eastern Nazarene Class of 2013!  We sent out a packet to you that included your receipt, a health form, and a link to an online roommate survey.  The health form is due by August 1st.  The roommate survey is how we figure out who to match you up with.  If you already know of an incoming freshman that you would like to room with there is also a place to write their name down there too.  Let me know if you have any questions about anything feel free to give me a call. Also keep July 17-18 open for VIP Orientation. Again we are extremely excited to have you as part of the incoming class of 2013.
